snippet.title: [JPN] Xenosaga Episode I Reloaded: Der Wille Zur Macht Featured Upgrades Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Xeno Museum - this project is meant to preserve as many digital video media/trailers/clips from the series as possible. Both Non subtitled and subtitled versions of trailers related to anything Xeno will be updated here in this playlist for all to enjoy and will be updated periodically.

Game: Xenosaga Episode I Reloaded: Der Wille Zur Macht
Difficulty of Gameplay: GREATEST RPG TRILOGY IN EXISTENCE
